OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781053389
OL,3,CNasa reveals Artemis III crew as it
OL,4,Cprepares for permanent moon base
OL,6,FNasa has revealed the four astronauts
OL,7,Fwho will take part in Artemis III as
OL,8,Fpart of the space agency's long-term
OL,9,Fgoal to establish a permanent human
OL,10,Fpresence on the Moon.
OL,12,FThe crew, set to launch as soon as
OL,13,Flate 2027, includes three Nasa
OL,14,Fastronauts: first-time space flier
OL,15,FAndre Douglas, astronaut Frank Rubio,
OL,16,Fveteran flier and test pilot Randy
OL,17,FBresnik. They will be joined by
OL,18,FItalian astronaut Luca Parmitano from
OL,19,Fthe European Space Agency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
