PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781053389
OL,3,CNasa reveals Artemis III crew as it
OL,4,Cprepares for permanent moon base
OL,6,FBresnik, who will command the mission,
OL,7,Fsaid during a press conference on
OL,8,FTuesday: "We are certainly humbled as
OL,9,Fa crew to be able to be your crew that
OL,10,Fexecutes this Artemis III mission in
OL,11,Fspace."
OL,13,FArtemis III is designed to serve as a
OL,14,Fprecursor mission to a Moon landing,
OL,15,Ftesting out how the Nasa-built Orion
OL,16,Fspacecraft will dock with a lunar
OL,17,Flander.
