PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781053389
OL,3,CNasa reveals Artemis III crew as it
OL,4,Cprepares for permanent moon base
OL,6,FThe primary goal of the flight, the
OL,7,Fspace agency says, is to "reduce risk"
OL,8,Fheading into an actual lunar
OL,9,Ftouchdown, which Nasa hopes will take
OL,10,Fplace as soon as 2028.
OL,12,FIt won't fly to the Moon; instead,
OL,13,Fthey'll orbit Earth while practising
OL,14,Fdocking their Orion capsule with two
OL,15,Flunar landers.
OL,17,FThe announcement came two months after
OL,18,FArtemis II's record-breaking trip
OL,19,Faround the moon that surpassed the
OL,20,Fdistance record of Apollo 13.
