CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781053389
OL,3,CNasa reveals Artemis III crew as it
OL,4,Cprepares for permanent moon base
OL,6,FElon Musk's SpaceX and Jeff Bezos'
OL,7,FBlue Origin are racing to deliver the
OL,8,Flunar landers.
OL,10,FBlue Origin suffered a recent setback
OL,11,Fwhen its massive rocket exploded
OL,12,Fduring an engine-firing test on the
OL,13,Flaunch pad in Florida, shaking nearby
OL,14,Fhomes and illuminating the sky with an
OL,15,Forange fireball.
OL,17,FNasa's Jeremy Parsons said the
OL,18,Fincident was a learning opportunity
OL,19,Fand that the space agency is confident
OL,20,FBlue Origin's rocket will be ready in
OL,21,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
