PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781053389
OL,3,CNasa reveals Artemis III crew as it
OL,4,Cprepares for permanent moon base
OL,6,FIn May, Nasa awarded hundreds of
OL,7,Fmillions of dollars in contracts to
OL,8,Ffour companies, including Blue Origin,
OL,9,Fto build landers, rovers and drones
OL,10,Ffor a future moon base.
OL,12,FNasa administrator Jared Isaacman said
OL,13,Fthe goal of the moon base is to lay
OL,14,Fthe foundation for a Mars expedition.
